What you need to know:

We know we are not perfect but we should try as much as we can if we are to protect our siblings. We are all aware that time is running out and if we do not learn to live with Covid-19, we will never get it right. Those already at Kasarani are the women’s rugby team - Lionesses, men’s rugby team - Shujaa, taekwondo and sprinters. As the numbers rise, let us ensure we are doing the right thing at the right time.